WEBVTT

00:00:04.010 --> 00:00:07.440
 haynt iz der tsvey un tsvantsikster detsember,

00:00:07.440 --> 00:00:09.675
toyznt nayn hundert nayntsik zeks.

00:00:10.002 --> 00:00:12.628
di ibergelebte iz Zhenye Raykhman,

00:00:12.735 --> 00:00:15.361
un der TAPE vet zayn der ferter, fir.

00:00:16.465 --> 00:00:21.521
azoy hot ir zikh opgeshtelt, dertseylt vegn ayer lebn vos iz forgekumen in dem dorf vu ir hot gearbet.

00:00:21.747 --> 00:00:26.975
zogt mir, ⟨ven ir⟩ zayt gekumen in dorf, zaynen geven a sakh mentshn, yidn, hot men gebrakht ahin?

00:00:26.185 --> 00:00:28.035
DA, UNK zeyer a sakh.

00:00:26.975 --> 00:00:30.329
nu, vifl, ⟨⟩, mishpokhes zaynen geven?

00:00:30.268 --> 00:00:33.687
efsher a, efsher a... ikh veys, efsher a dray hundert mishpokhes.

00:00:33.897 --> 00:00:36.743
un tsum ende, vifl zaynen geblibn?

00:00:33.913 --> 00:00:34.750
UNK

00:00:38.065 --> 00:00:39.797
az m'hot shoyn bafrayt aykh?

00:00:39.077 --> 00:00:42.243
i- ikh veys, az, az hundert mentshn iz groys.

00:00:42.452 --> 00:00:43.745
hundert mentshn?

00:00:43.617 --> 00:00:45.484
fun dray hundert FAMILIEN.

00:00:45.945 --> 00:00:47.525
APROXIMATIV.

00:00:48.759 --> 00:00:53.561
 vos nokh kent ir dertseyln vegn dem lebn vos iz bay aykh gevezn beys ir zayt gevezn

00:00:53.387 --> 00:00:54.495
⟨un der-⟩...

00:00:53.561 --> 00:00:55.507
in dem geto in dem dorf?

00:00:55.868 --> 00:01:04.029
un dernokh dem, dos iz geven shoyn dem le- ⟨dem⟩, dos letste yor, ho'mir geha- gehat a bisl HILFE fun Tshernevits, vayl dortn iz geblibn a,

00:01:04.086 --> 00:01:06.167
a shvester fun mayn mame.

00:01:06.167 --> 00:01:09.860
farholfn tsu blaybn hot farholfn eyner a,

00:01:09.860 --> 00:01:12.645
a, vi me zogt, a ZEMLYAK, a...

00:01:12.645 --> 00:01:16.702
velkhe in eynem hobn ge-, gevaksn, in eynem gelernt...

00:01:16.708 --> 00:01:20.202
un der mentsh, er hot geheysn Popovitsh,

00:01:20.202 --> 00:01:23.277
iz gevorn, fun Tshernevits iz er gevorn,

00:01:23.277 --> 00:01:25.218
azoy vi me zogt, birger-mayster.

00:01:25.218 --> 00:01:27.810
er iz geven a groyser mentsh un ⟨z- er⟩ hot getun

00:01:27.810 --> 00:01:29.268
zeyer a sakh far di yidn.

00:01:29.268 --> 00:01:31.740
er fleg zey aroysgibn AUTORISATIONEN,

00:01:31.740 --> 00:01:34.481
az dermit zol men kenen blaybn oyfn ort.

00:01:34.481 --> 00:01:35.386
dos heyst,

00:01:35.386 --> 00:01:37.559
WERTVOLLE JUDEN hot er zey gemakht.

00:01:38.140 --> 00:01:44.479
er iz, di sh-, mayn tante, mayn mame's shvester, zi hot geheysn Royze Miler.

00:01:44.603 --> 00:01:47.983
zi iz geven shoyn oyfn, oyf der STATION,

00:01:47.983 --> 00:01:53.391
in di, in tsug mit di kinder, mit di eydems, mit di, mitn man,

00:01:53.391 --> 00:01:56.223
un di mekhutonim. ale zenen geven shoyn in tsug.

00:01:56.382 --> 00:02:01.126
zi hot zikh, ir iz gelungen ibertsugibn dem Popovitsh, dem,

00:02:01.126 --> 00:02:04.183
 birger-mayster fun der shtot,

00:02:04.183 --> 00:02:08.013
er zol hel- ⟨"gey mir helfn!"⟩ az er ken un az er vil,

00:02:08.013 --> 00:02:09.009
vos zi

00:02:09.009 --> 00:02:10.415
deportirt men.

00:02:10.945 --> 00:02:12.491
s'iz tsugekumen

00:02:12.649 --> 00:02:13.689
tsun im,

00:02:13.898 --> 00:02:15.292
ot dos tsetl,

00:02:15.687 --> 00:02:19.781
iz er gekumen OHNE WEITERES oyfn BAHNHOF,

00:02:20.175 --> 00:02:23.835
un hot zey ale aroysgenumen: zi, di sh- di,

00:02:23.835 --> 00:02:25.455
di, mayn tante,

00:02:25.455 --> 00:02:29.062
 mit ire mekhutonim, mit di kinder.

00:02:29.187 --> 00:02:32.835
aroysgenumen ale un zogt, "geyt tsurik in ayere heymen."

00:02:33.085 --> 00:02:39.004
un azoy hot er getun, der mentsh, der, der Popovitsh, hot getun far a sakh yidn azoy: AUTORISATIONEN

00:02:39.004 --> 00:02:40.554
gemakht, ⟨SO⟩ vayter.

00:02:40.628 --> 00:02:44.452
ot o di, tante, zi iz geven in Tshernevits.

00:02:44.458 --> 00:02:47.557
der man hot gearbet oyf a guter arbet.

00:02:48.154 --> 00:02:54.177
 un, hot, ⟨i- m-⟩ undz ho'mir gekent ⟨k- key- k-⟩, makhn a

00:02:54.177 --> 00:02:56.551
farbindung keyn Tshernevits.

00:02:56.625 --> 00:02:58.759
vi azoy ho'mir gemakht a farbindung?

00:02:58.759 --> 00:03:00.722
dos iz oykh shoyn geven dos letste yor.

00:03:00.722 --> 00:03:04.263
s'hot zikh tsuzamengenumen etlekhe, FAMILIEN,

00:03:04.422 --> 00:03:05.701
f- meydlekh,

00:03:05.701 --> 00:03:07.456
vayblekh, mener,

00:03:07.456 --> 00:03:09.937
un m'iz gegangen keyn ⟨Mogilev-Podolsk⟩.

00:03:09.937 --> 00:03:13.651
m'hot gevust az in ⟨Mogilev-Podolsk⟩ ken men krign dem,

00:03:13.651 --> 00:03:14.844
di farbindung,

00:03:14.844 --> 00:03:18.449
vayl dortn, fun dortn kumt men, ahin kumen di,

00:03:18.449 --> 00:03:21.627
 kuryers, un fun dortn ken men krign...

00:03:21.627 --> 00:03:25.147
un dortn hob ikh gevust az, hob ikh nokh kuzinen in, in

00:03:25.147 --> 00:03:26.395
⟨Mogilev-Podolsk⟩.

00:03:26.629 --> 00:03:30.701
⟨un⟩ zi iz geven zeyer, aza kluge un ales... zi iz geven elter fun mir,

00:03:30.701 --> 00:03:34.402
elter fun mir... un zi vet helfn, tomer ikh'l zi gefinen.

00:03:34.813 --> 00:03:37.442
ikh hob mikh ayngeshlosn mit di, mit der

00:03:37.442 --> 00:03:40.781
kompanyon, mit di etlekhe mentshn. geven a zeks mentshn.

00:03:41.648 --> 00:03:46.755
un eyne a kristlekhe froy hot zikh untergenumen tsu firn,

00:03:47.048 --> 00:03:49.084
zayn a firerin.

00:03:49.714 --> 00:03:56.846
undz ze'mir ongekumen, mit ir. zi geyt foroys; zi veyst dem veg. dos darf men tsvontsik kilometer geyn durkhn vald.

00:03:58.101 --> 00:04:03.329
undz, gey'mir, nor yeder shorkh, yedes feygele vos se git a fli durkh,

00:04:03.329 --> 00:04:04.451
a bletele,

00:04:04.451 --> 00:04:05.818
falt aroys di neshome.

00:04:05.818 --> 00:04:08.878
zi geyt foroys un me hert shtime⟨n⟩ redn.

00:04:09.289 --> 00:04:13.831
undz ho'mir shtark moyre gehat, es zol nisht kumen di POLIZEI, ⟨zol⟩ nisht ⟨di⟩ zhandarn.

00:04:14.166 --> 00:04:20.572
vos meynt ir? s'iz shoyn geven azoy vesne-tsayt. mentshn, a teyl, hobn shoyn gearbet, in gortn, di BAUERn.

00:04:21.861 --> 00:04:27.910
kumt akegn, k-, zi loyft foroys. zogt zi, "ikh'l geyn," zogt zi, "ikh'l geyn zen ver s'iz,

00:04:27.910 --> 00:04:29.803
un tomer s'iz epes azoy, vel ikh redn."

00:04:30.079 --> 00:04:33.043
vos meynt ir? zi ho- iz gegangen foroys,

00:04:33.066 --> 00:04:38.887
un hot bagegnt di POLIZEI, un hot undz oysgegibn, vos s'iz yidn.

00:04:40.339 --> 00:04:42.842
⟨un d-⟩ un dernokh dem, zi hot zikh shoyn mer nisht gevizn.

00:04:42.842 --> 00:04:47.573
un zi hot zikh shoyn mer nisht gevizn. un ⟨mir⟩ ze'mir, di POLIZEI hoybt on tsu zukhn vu m'iz,

00:04:47.573 --> 00:04:49.112
un dortn hot a BAUER,

00:04:49.112 --> 00:04:52.123
a BAU-... undz ho'mir zikh shoyn gegibn ⟨a, ho'mir⟩ gezen az dos iz nisht keyn...

00:04:52.123 --> 00:04:55.876
geven eltere mentshn un kluge, kluge mentshn, hobn teykef farshtanen

00:04:55.876 --> 00:04:57.059
az dos iz nisht keyn,

00:04:57.059 --> 00:05:00.431
⟨, dos iz a, nisht, nisht, s'iz nisht,⟩ nisht keyn gute zakh.

00:05:00.454 --> 00:05:01.528
az zi hot...

00:05:00.505 --> 00:05:02.209
⟨s'iz a⟩ gefar far aykh?

00:05:01.737 --> 00:05:04.718
yo. dos iz, hot zi undz oysgegibn.

00:05:04.808 --> 00:05:08.109
⟨undz⟩ UNK ⟨in de⟩r zayt. iz geven aza OVRAG,

00:05:08.470 --> 00:05:12.491
ho'mir zikh ale aropgelozt in dem OVRAG, ⟨un m'hot, s'iz⟩ geven in vald,

00:05:12.491 --> 00:05:16.604
un di bleter hobn undz fardekt un mir ze'mir gelegn di gantse tsayt dortn.

00:05:16.604 --> 00:05:19.382
der POLIZEI geyt zukhn undz.

00:05:19.523 --> 00:05:22.354
un dortn epes a alter, ⟨o⟩rl,

00:05:22.354 --> 00:05:26.531
 a alter, krist, zit-, a-, arbet in gortn.

00:05:26.531 --> 00:05:27.468
fregt er,

00:05:27.468 --> 00:05:28.875
"vu zenen do di,

00:05:28.875 --> 00:05:29.891
vu zenen di..."

00:05:29.891 --> 00:05:31.813
der krist aleyn hot undz gezogt.

00:05:31.813 --> 00:05:33.762
"UTEKAYTE!" zogt er.

00:05:33.762 --> 00:05:38.377
"SPRYA⟨CH⟩'TES'!" ⟨,⟩ vayl, z- zogt er, vayl s'iz a, POLIZEIEN.

00:05:38.377 --> 00:05:42.100
"vu?" zogt er "ahin, geyts arop in dem OVRA-..." er hot undz geholfn.

00:05:42.100 --> 00:05:43.620
s'iz dortn nisht keyn shlekhte

00:05:43.620 --> 00:05:44.543
kristn do.

00:05:45.291 --> 00:05:48.961
un er kumt, der POLIZEI: "vu zenen zey? vu zenen zey?"

00:05:48.961 --> 00:05:50.060
un der

00:05:50.185 --> 00:05:51.866
krist hot gevizn...

00:05:51.906 --> 00:05:53.790
"vu zenen zey gegangen? zog!"

00:05:53.830 --> 00:05:59.123
zogt er, "ahin." undz ze'mir gegangen, er hot undz geshikt aher, zogt er "ahin." hot er ⟨im op⟩gefirt ahin.

00:05:59.196 --> 00:06:01.884
er geyt ⟨un zukht mit dem geve- gever⟩.

00:06:01.884 --> 00:06:03.976
ze'mir opgezesn in dem,

00:06:03.976 --> 00:06:06.930
unter di bleter in dem, in dem,

00:06:06.930 --> 00:06:09.146
in der YAMA dortn hintn,

00:06:09.270 --> 00:06:10.465
a nakht.

00:06:10.465 --> 00:06:11.534
far tog,

00:06:11.534 --> 00:06:13.668
far tog UNK ⟨ho'mir⟩ gemuzt geyn.

00:06:13.978 --> 00:06:17.891
mir kum'mir in vald, azoy in tsentral vald. me kumt aroyf: vi azoy ken men,

00:06:17.891 --> 00:06:21.193
vi azoy ken men geyn? stetshke aher, stetshke ahin. yede stetshke

00:06:21.193 --> 00:06:22.730
firt oyf a andern veg.

00:06:23.277 --> 00:06:28.311
i- hob ikh mikh nokh ongerufn. ⟨ikh bin nokh⟩ geven az-, nokh yung, nor, ⟨ikh veys⟩, der seykhl hot ⟨fartrogn⟩. zog ikh,

00:06:28.311 --> 00:06:30.285
"ir veyst vos? dos iz a shtot,

00:06:30.285 --> 00:06:34.248
un dos iz derfer. ir zet, do zenen nisht oysgetretene azoyne

00:06:34.248 --> 00:06:35.136
stetshkes.

00:06:35.136 --> 00:06:38.812
kumts, vel'mir geyn oyf der stetshke vu s'iz am bestn oysgetretn.

00:06:39.004 --> 00:06:40.213
s'iz a shtot," zog ikh.

00:06:40.540 --> 00:06:45.174
zogt, ⟨⟩, "RICHTIG. klug, a klug meydele." UNK. un m'iz gegangen oyf dem o,

00:06:45.771 --> 00:06:52.651
oyf der stetshke. mir kum'mir on biz keyn ⟨Mogilev-Podolsk⟩, biz s'iz shoyn ongehoybn likhtik tsu vern. dos iz ales azoy

00:06:52.651 --> 00:06:53.561
in der tunkl.

00:06:53.601 --> 00:06:56.683
kumt akegn a g- oykhet epes a elterer man,

00:06:56.723 --> 00:06:58.134
a krist,

00:06:58.191 --> 00:07:00.487
 freg'mir, ⟨s'iz, mir ho'mir sh-⟩ freg'mir,

00:07:00.487 --> 00:07:03.787
"vi azoy ken'mir araynkumen, in dem ⟨Mogilev-Podolsk⟩?"

00:07:03.827 --> 00:07:07.806
zogt er,... un do geyt aza vaser a groys...

00:07:07.806 --> 00:07:11.217
zogt er, "dortn geyts nisht, un do zolt ir nisht geyn, dortn zolt ir ⟨geyn⟩,

00:07:11.217 --> 00:07:14.886
⟨iz⟩, vayl dortn zenen daytshn, dortn iz militerishe daytshn, do-...

00:07:14.886 --> 00:07:18.294
geyts," zogt er, "azoy az ir zolt kenen araynfaln in geto."

00:07:18.294 --> 00:07:19.801
s'iz dortn nokh geven a geto.

00:07:20.179 --> 00:07:21.374
iz azoy geven.

00:07:21.374 --> 00:07:24.828
oyf dem geto, azoy der o ⟨t-⟩ krist hot undz ongevizn,

00:07:24.828 --> 00:07:26.222
in dem geto

00:07:26.222 --> 00:07:31.836
hot men, yidn nokh epes gehandlt: tishlekh geven, broyt hot men farkoyft.

00:07:31.836 --> 00:07:33.100
un me geyt.

00:07:33.100 --> 00:07:37.858
plutsem flit arayn a mototsikl, ⟨, ⟩, dortn vu di yidn handlen, un di tishlekh mit di UNK,

00:07:37.858 --> 00:07:39.676
mit zeyere skhoyre,

00:07:39.676 --> 00:07:43.528
mit a mototsikl ales ibergekert. s'iz gevorn ⟨g-⟩ gornisht derfun.

00:07:43.770 --> 00:07:45.747
dernokh dem, nokh dem ale...

00:07:44.631 --> 00:07:46.144
ver iz dos gevezn?

00:07:45.747 --> 00:07:48.759
a, a daytsh. zbitkes gemakht.

00:07:49.558 --> 00:07:56.909
un dernokh dem, dos ales hot ⟨men⟩ gezen. ODN- ODNAKO, dernokh dem ⟨hot men⟩ zikh tsurik tsuzamen. s'iz azoy vi a bazar; men trogt tsu farkoyfn.

00:07:57.203 --> 00:08:00.136
ikh hoyb on nokhtsufregn azoy un azoy, di un di.

00:08:00.136 --> 00:08:03.659
zogt er, "yo. zey lebn dortn, dortn zenen do, zenen do."

00:08:03.784 --> 00:08:08.148
un, un ikh tref punkt a, fun dem onkl a shvester oykh oyf dem bazar.

00:08:08.610 --> 00:08:10.209
"oy-vey!

00:08:10.209 --> 00:08:14.240
kum, kh'vel dikh tsufirn." zi hot tsugefo- -firt tsu der

00:08:14.466 --> 00:08:15.590
kuzine.

00:08:15.732 --> 00:08:17.635
zi iz geven a tante fun der,

00:08:17.635 --> 00:08:19.095
funem foter's zayt,

00:08:19.095 --> 00:08:20.428
fun der kuzine.

00:08:20.428 --> 00:08:24.613
zi iz sh- di, zi iz shoyn geven a, a, vi me zogt, a NICHTE tsun ir.

00:08:24.613 --> 00:08:27.639
zi hot mikh tsugefirt ahin. ikh bin geven a yung meydele.

00:08:27.747 --> 00:08:31.976
azoy ⟨min shtark f-,⟩ shlekht gekukt zikh, aza min

00:08:32.082 --> 00:08:34.511
DISTROFIK, tsart.

00:08:35.087 --> 00:08:41.358
 z- hot zi mikh tsugefirt. ⟨mir kum'mir, hot men⟩ zikh ongehoybn baym kop. m'hot mikh, ibergetun,

00:08:41.414 --> 00:08:43.163
 ⟨hot mikh⟩ opgebodn,

00:08:43.169 --> 00:08:45.133
 m'⟨hot mikh⟩ opgeshoyrn,

00:08:45.133 --> 00:08:47.909
un ⟨ikh hob⟩ gehat a bisl a ponem vi a mentsh.

00:08:47.909 --> 00:08:50.302
m'hot mikh gehaltn dortn akht teg.

00:08:50.730 --> 00:08:56.967
di goye iz aheymgegangen tsurik in dorf un hot gezogt, zi hot gehert shisn; di mentshn ⟨zenen⟩ ale oysgeshosn.

00:08:57.160 --> 00:08:58.843
i- un ikh oykh.

00:08:58.843 --> 00:09:02.367
m'hot mikh b- baveynt. m'iz ge- m'iz gezesn shive

00:09:02.745 --> 00:09:03.566
nokh mir.

00:09:04.467 --> 00:09:10.426
un ikh bin dervayl akht teg do. do, b- vasht men zikh, un me hot mikh opgevashn, me git mir esn.

00:09:10.426 --> 00:09:14.054
di, ⟨d- d-⟩ kuzine hot gehat a kuryer,

00:09:14.054 --> 00:09:15.058
velkher fleg

00:09:15.199 --> 00:09:16.773
geyn keyn ⟨Mogilev⟩

00:09:16.773 --> 00:09:18.107
un kumen ahin.

00:09:18.107 --> 00:09:22.179
un mit dem kuryer hot er gebrakht gelt far a sakh yidn dortn.

00:09:22.253 --> 00:09:24.660
un bay ir, zi hot dos gefirt.

00:09:24.750 --> 00:09:25.945
zi iz itstert in,

00:09:25.945 --> 00:09:27.056
in Kanade.

00:09:27.079 --> 00:09:28.845
zi makht oykh zeyer a sakh

00:09:28.851 --> 00:09:30.296
guts itster far der,

00:09:30.353 --> 00:09:32.449
 far ISRAEL. zi f⟨ri-⟩ zi firt

00:09:32.449 --> 00:09:34.728
halbe milyonen gelt keyn ISRAEL.

00:09:34.728 --> 00:09:36.457
zi makht farshidene,

00:09:36.457 --> 00:09:41.602
nu, dortn oysshtelungen tsi AU- AUCTION; ales geyt far ISRAEL.

00:09:42.216 --> 00:09:44.775
OBSHCHEM, ot o di kuzine

00:09:45.203 --> 00:09:46.880
hot geholfn.

00:09:47.920 --> 00:09:49.382
undz ho'mir gehat

00:09:49.489 --> 00:09:50.713
gelt yede,

00:09:50.713 --> 00:09:52.894
tsvey hundert mark a monat fleg zi shikn.

00:09:52.894 --> 00:09:53.821
ho'mir gehat

00:09:53.821 --> 00:09:55.299
far der ⟨voynort⟩ tsu batsoln.

00:09:55.299 --> 00:09:58.058
mir ho'mir gekent shoyn lebn. ven nisht di tante,

00:09:58.058 --> 00:09:59.458
⟨voltn⟩ mir oysgegangen,

00:09:59.458 --> 00:10:00.678
⟨iz dos zikher⟩.

00:10:00.373 --> 00:10:03.371
zogt mir, ir hot gelebt in a,

00:10:03.698 --> 00:10:07.269
in a kvartir, ikh meyn in a hoyz hot ir gelebt, bay...?

00:10:06.145 --> 00:10:09.467
