00:10:09.385 --> 00:10:11.434
on⟨e⟩...

00:10:09.467 --> 00:10:10.188
gelegn.

00:10:11.434 --> 00:10:15.302
in dem klub vu ⟨z-⟩ ir zayt geven UNK ⟨zayt ir fun dortn⟩ avekgeforn?

00:10:13.722 --> 00:10:15.246
UNK

